title: How To Activate magicJackGO | magicJack
description:
Learn how to activate your magicJackGO with this instructional video and follow the steps below to set it up and save!

0:22 Step 1: Plug the ethernet cord into the magicJackGO's Internet port.
0:36 Step 2: Plug the other end of the ethernet cord into your modem or router. 
0:51 Step 3: Plug your phone into magicJackGO in the Phone port.
1:00 Step 4: Plug the power adapter into the magicJackGO.
1:04 Step 5: Plug the power adapter into the electrical outlet.
1:14 Step 6: Visit mjreg.com to register your magicJackGO.
1:23 Troubleshooting magicJackGO issues.
